{"tid":864190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟創辦人保羅艾倫淋巴癌復發逝世 終年65歲","createTime":"2018-10-16T04:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T06:59:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db7c687e2159073ffc6c6449981cec96c58d83d8","tid":864190,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"美國微軟公司創辦人之一、億萬富翁保羅艾倫（Paul Allen）周一因癌病在西雅圖逝世，終年65歲。<br />\n保羅艾倫成立的公司Vulcan Inc公佈他的死訊。<br />\n保羅艾倫的妹妹喬迪（Jody）發表聲明，讚揚兄長成就非凡，「大眾認識的保羅艾倫是科技人和慈善家，對我們而言他是親愛的兄長或叔叔，也是的與別不同的朋友」。<br />\n微軟讚揚保羅艾倫對微軟、業界及社區的貢獻都不可或缺，「他默默耕耘，創造出神奇的產品、經驗與研究機構，改變了世界」。<br />\n保羅艾倫本月初證實淋巴癌復發，當時他說「我和我的醫生都感到十分樂觀，醫學發展一日千里，我會積極抗癌」。<br />\n保羅艾倫於1975年與好友蓋茨（Bill Gates）創辦微軟，但於1983年因患上霍奇金氏淋巴瘤（Hodgkin's Lymphoma）而離開微軟。2009年他罹患非霍奇金氏淋巴瘤（non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma)，今年復發，是他第三次患癌。<br />\n坐擁逾205億美元（1,599億港元）身家的保羅艾倫，今年在福布斯全球富豪排行榜排第44，是美國西雅圖的大慈善家，資助無數研究，亦大力支持環保、教育和科技發展。<br />\n保羅艾倫亦擁有數支球隊，包括NBA的波特蘭拓荒者和NFL的西雅圖海鷹。他於1986年成立Vulcan Inc管理旗下以億萬元計的生意和慈善事業。「我有信心在治療期間，領導團隊能繼續帶領公司業務發展。」他說。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181016/large/1539651329_f94d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181016%2Flarge%2F1539651329_f94d.jpg&h=672dd299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181016/58798984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58798984&d=MCtIC93QByPSCqUAHvyvcS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=32214539\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58798984&h=47e471f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181016/58798984</a>"},{"pid":"f2f4e21e8add1970cb1f5b80bda2e927fd4a7022","tid":864190,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"95a05f61c72ae710452ef07d2d462ee43e637f40","tid":864190,"uid":205587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2f4e21e8add1970cb1f5b80bda2e927fd4a7022","tid":864190,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"抵死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"23e99f6e7eca2acd2853fdb71e6e0e1bdecf69d3","tid":864190,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:30:16.000Z","msg":"好後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6875edd103fca95fb5bad73e3ddc0e83d17d1774","tid":864190,"uid":55200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"所以有錢買不到健康，時間。<br />\n連登仔已經俾好多人富有，做多啲有意義事吧，<br />\n不要成日上網打j 圍爐"},{"pid":"08824e0b20c4574f159c7a61a636ed86681c3ed0","tid":864190,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"波特籣拓荒者要搵風水佬睇睇"},{"pid":"5392207240e4b760a3b069ec5d745cf4356cf842","tid":864190,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08824e0b20c4574f159c7a61a636ed86681c3ed0","tid":864190,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"波特籣拓荒者要搵風水佬睇睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"奧登，roy，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}